# Marin Chatbot

A romantic AI chatbot featuring Marin Kitagawa persona with Text-to-Speech (TTS) capabilities.

## Features

- Chat interface with Marin Kitagawa (from My Dress-Up Darling)
- Text-to-Speech using Kokoro TTS
- Image upload and description capabilities
- Romantic and affectionate responses
- Vibe detection (lovely/angry) affecting TTS tone

## Installation

```bash
pip install .
```

## Usage

```bash
marin-chat
```

Or run directly:

```bash
python app.py
```

Then open your browser to `http://localhost:5069`

## Requirements

- Python 3.8+
- Kokoro TTS installed and available in PATH
- GEMINI_API_KEY environment variable set for AI responses

## Configuration

Set your Gemini API key:

```bash
export GEMINI_API_KEY="your_api_key_here"
```

## Project Structure

- `app.py` - Main Flask application
- `marin.py` - Marin's personality and AI interaction logic
- `image.py` - Image processing (Leo) for describing uploaded images
- `static/` - Static files (CSS, JS, uploads, generated images)
- `templates/` - HTML templates

